{"tid":1427060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文攻武鬥","createTime":"2019-08-07T04:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:45:31.000Z","uid":164792,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e335585c5d781125a737e3fb094c347b25b49844","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:50:13.000Z","msg":"文攻<br />\n1.四點的記者招待會反有利君雅幫我地做攻勢，所以記者招待會反而變成我們文宣武器，因為謝振中問到口啞啞，變相顯得警方隱藏真相凸顯出政府的不是。<br />\n<br />\n2.文宣長輩圖必定繼續！民間記者招待會要有專業觀感，頭盔口罩不能少，最好有一位民主派議員坐鎮，以議員對抗警司。<br />\n<br />\n對準政權<br />\n1.和理非長期進駐機場，癱瘓機場。<br />\n<br />\n智取狗隻<br />\n2.be Water睇得出狗隻開始崩潰，失控。<br />\n每日都要玩。少食多餐。重量不重質。<br />\n先引狗，開始周街遊走，玩追逐戰消耗嘅體力。<br />\n我哋，人數優，裝備輕，負重輕。相反狗出動full gear 。例如尋日嘅深水埗需要係深水埗遊走。<br />\n<br />\n武鬥休班<br />\n3.一次麻包袋成功就夠，心理壓力極大，擔心會否下個就係我。"},{"pid":"2adb00451950d6629bf617c2518301d2a9c39be5","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:50:58.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"b1b81ef61148e8957f01dd130c81cc412a64692b","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:51:19.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c868837b48f814df7d6d07d5f2d94222f69509aa","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"26c9effed9f5347d1a2e771255f7901b95b0b9fb","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:39.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6ac119078ca1836b033e43027ade85298bb56a7e","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e3605792948d8e20fe6a8caae44e846b06097137","tid":1427060,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:55:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db2d5e0d2a144ae708cb1b136dc659d6098f667a","tid":1427060,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:56:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"6ef3d40f1e5